FBIS3-60308 "jpten001___94089" JPRS-TEN-94-001 Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Environmental Issues 13 January 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA UKRAINE Government Adopts Resolution on Environmental Protection WS0501142894 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in Ukrainian 1100 GMT 5 Jan 93 WS0501142894 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network Language: Ukrainian Article Type:BFN [Text] The Cabinet of Ministers of Ukraine has approved a resolution on procedures for conducting state registration in the field of atmospheric air protection. The state's executive authorities, enterprises, departments, and organizations, regardless of their ownership status, are obliged to comply with the resolution. The document emphasizes that the main goals of state registration in the field of atmospheric air protection are collecting data on facilities that contribute or may contribute to atmospheric pollution, making assessments on the volume of harmful substances emitted into the atmosphere, and evaluating the influence of different physical and biological factors on air pollution.
